<a name="apothic_robe"></a>
<font color="#FFFFFF" face="Arial">
<strong>Apothic Robe - AC 11</strong>
<font size=-1></font><BR>
Slot: <a href="/armour/chest.shtml">Chest</a><BR>
Weight: 1.0 - DEF, ERU, GNM, HIE, HUM<BR>
Classes: <a href="/magician/armour/chest.shtml">MAG</a><BR>
<font color=red>
(Magic) (No Drop) <BR>
(STA +12) (DEX +5) (INT +14) (Mana +40) </font>
<BR>
Dropped in the Plane of Hate by Male Revenants.<BR>

